Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 好頭痛 簡直...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受 我的視線都模糊不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要再播放一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你記憶中一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是用瑞典語交談
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你完全不會說瑞典語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是聽得懂一些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不會 媽咪 我不會說瑞典語
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你說的是英語
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還說到冷原子實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷原子實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說他們在做一項實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我說...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保羅在做一項實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 問題是 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生意外前 我對冷原子實驗毫無印象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對那項實驗毫無印象 我不...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亨利說那個東西跟什么物理學有關
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一項量子實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要用來捕捉量子疊加形態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是量子疊加狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:05:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指同一件東西能同時出現在兩個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個寫著你名字的卡帶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要聽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的日期是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“2021年10月15日”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是意外發生后隔天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休士頓 我想知道將尸體運返地球的流程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空站 你有什么擔憂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:05:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的擔憂是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的擔憂是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利遜的傷口嚴重裂開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心尸體搬進救生艙后 一旦離開零重力...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許沒必要聽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我只需要想個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽咪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去做些意大利面 然后一起抱抱 接著...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽咪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我跟以前一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的愛麗絲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我... - 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 別這么說 你不用道歉 不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是覺得你不像我的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不像你媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們必須想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是需要想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你通知艾琳娜了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在路上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她來干嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她會負責照顧你太太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 那你又來干嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那部機器對人有害無利 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來是因為這事也曾發生在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(美國宇航局)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 寶貝 說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么躲在櫥柜里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 寶貝  - 我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞起來像你的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然像誰的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會有點刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你很快就暖和起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 熱水沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去給你燒些熱水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 我好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽咪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲  我在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 你去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在那邊 在外面的大雪中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從外面回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她找到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今她又消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 如果你真看到她... 我知道你以為看到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感受得到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感受得到她的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聞到她的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感受到雪的觸感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 她剛剛就在那邊 - 她不在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 她剛剛就在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 趕緊讓你暖和起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后回到床上睡覺 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 她在哪里  - 誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒看到自己嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是指鏡子中嗎  - 不是 在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽咪 我什么都沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去換衣服 那邊還有一間小木屋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們的小木屋一樣 但不是我們的小木屋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是跟卡帶有關
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊穿上雪地裝備 我們要過湖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽咪 我對我說過的話向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽咪 我不是有意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我們趕緊回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她剛剛躲在樓上的櫥柜里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太冷了 她會凍死的 我們得趕緊找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么情況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條路徹底堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那趕緊去弄個鏟雪機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在路上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒被困在另一邊 我太太瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽咪 我覺得另一間小木屋不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定是這個方向
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人難過時可能會看到幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些到過外太空的人都會看到幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想傷害你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不想讓你難過 但我認為你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為你不是我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果我不是你的女兒 那你又是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我媽咪做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起找出真相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲
